Pretty sure

 > Vendor Dependency ReduxLib has invalid year 2025. Expected to be 2024. Reach out to the vendor to get a new version of the dependency. Attempting to modify an existing dependency will break at runtime, and will result in loss of support from the WPILib team.

Is your error. I think you have the 2025 version of redux library installed. Take a look at the installing vendor libraries page to see how to uninstall 2025, and then install 2024. The 2024 vendor dep url for redux is:

https://frcsdk.reduxrobotics.com/ReduxLib_2024.json
